extracted_content.content:
[![Image 1: logo](https://www.wachete.com/img/logo.svg)](https://www.wachete.com/)

Monitor  
web changes  
easy peasy
----------------------------------

1.  Select area to monitor on URL address
2.  Set monitoring interval
3.  Get notified

![Image 2: hero](https://www.wachete.com/img/hero.svg)

![Image 3: mobile-hero](https://www.wachete.com/img/mobile-hero.svg)

How it works?
-------------

Take a look at how Wachete works in action.

[![Image 4: Wachete tutorial](https://www.wachete.com/img/youtube.webp)](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UFgE6vewuj4)

* * *

Use cases
---------

With Wachete you can easily automate repetitive tasks and save time in your daily life or in your business.

![Image 5: useCase](https://www.wachete.com/img/useCases/useCase1.svg)

### Buy at the best price

As a shopper, never miss the opportunity to buy at the lowest price.

![Image 6: useCase](https://www.wachete.com/img/useCases/useCase2.svg)

### Track competition

As a store owner, easily monitor at what price the competition is selling the same products as you do.

![Image 7: useCase](https://www.wachete.com/img/useCases/useCase3.svg)

### Defacement detection

As a web administrator, make sure that nobody replaces the content on your page without your knowledge.

![Image 8: useCase](https://www.wachete.com/img/useCases/useCase4.svg)

### Website health check

As a website owner, know when one of your web pages is not available.

![Image 9: useCase](https://www.wachete.com/img/useCases/useCase5.svg)

### Website audit changes

As a company providing law compliance audits, get notified when your customers modify the content on their website.

![Image 10: useCase](https://www.wachete.com/img/useCases/useCase6.svg)

### New job openings

As a recruiter, receive notifications when companies post new job offers.

* * *

Sample wachets
--------------

We prepared several wachets to inspire you. Just click on it to see details or add it to your own list.

###### Careers | Slack

#### 7Open positions

3 days ago

###### Week number Europe

#### 16 16

yesterday

###### Sunset, San Francisco, California, U.S.A.

#### 19:44

6 hours ago

###### UK Singles Top 1

#### Ordinary Alex Warren

21 days ago

###### Nameday - Czech republic

#### Vincenc, Vincent

23 hours ago

###### iDNES.cz

#### Rapidní nárůst nemocných žloutenkou v Praze, MHD už dezinfikují plošně

17 hours ago

* * *

Features
--------

We provide a large variety of features and are constantly adding new ones. Is there a feature you miss? Do not hesitate to [get in touch with us.](mailto:info@wachete.com)

*   Monitor password protected pages
*   We monitor pages using proxy servers in different locations
*   Send daily or weekly summary email with changes from several pages
*   Monitor specific part of the web page
*   Monitor whole web page including crawled sub-pages
*   Collect history, changes and web content up to 12 months
*   View numeric data in graphs
*   Monitor dynamic and javascript pages
*   Download data as excel sheet
*   Setup clever email and mobile notifications when content has changed
*   Create RSS feed from content of any page
*   Monitor availability of web pages.
*   Monitor updates of text in PDF, MS Word, DOCX, XLSX files or JSON on the web or track files size changes.
*   [REST interface for 3rd party partners](https://www.wachete.com/api)
*   Discover integrations with other products and apps using [Zapier](https://zapier.com/apps/wachete/integrations). [Learn more](https://www.wachete.com/zapier-integrations)

![Image 11: features](https://www.wachete.com/img/features.svg)

Mobile Apps
-----------

No matter where you are, you can always monitor your wachets and get notified.

[![Image 12: apple](https://www.wachete.com/img/apps/apple.png)](https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/wachete/id1007508842)[![Image 13: microsoft](https://www.wachete.com/img/apps/microsoft.png)](https://apps.microsoft.com/detail/9wzdncrdf82l?hl=en-US&gl=US)[![Image 14: google](https://www.wachete.com/img/apps/google.png)](https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.wachete.client)

Browser extensions
------------------

Easily add new pages to monitor thru the following browser extensions.

[![Image 15: chrome](https://www.wachete.com/img/apps/001-chrome.png)](https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/wachete-monitor-website-c/oendfdlboglnmpmlpnokgopffmiphfgn)

[![Image 16: firefox](https://www.wachete.com/img/apps/002-firefox.png)](https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/wachete-monitor-web-changes/)

[![Image 17: edge](https://www.wachete.com/img/apps/003-microsoft.png)](https://microsoftedge.microsoft.com/addons/detail/wachete-monitor-website/ndmcpgbodbijngkkgekmdmkkabkjmccd)

![Image 18: app-bg](https://www.wachete.com/img/apps-wave.svg)
